hi, I was trying to create a campaign on my account but its not going through what could be the issue

Hey there! Let's figure out what's going on with your campaign. Could you let me know if you've checked the following: 
- Campaign start date 
- Bidding type 
- Targeting or budget settings 
- Any recent changes in the last 72 hours? 
Once we have this information, we can look into it further. If you need more help, feel free to reach out!
I'm trying to create a fresh ads campaign but its not letting me do it

Let's get your campaign up and running! Here are a few things to check:
1. Make sure you're hitting 'Save and Next' instead of just 'Save' at the Campaign and Ad set level.
2. Verify that you have a valid payment method associated with your account, even if you're using ad credits.
3. Ensure the landing page URL doesn't capitalize the 'h' in 'http://' or 'https://'.

If you've checked these and still face issues, let me know!
I'm here to help with whatever you need! Let me know your question, and I'll do my best to assist you right away.
You cant help me with the type of issue I have

I understand your frustration. If you could provide more details about the issue, I'll do my best to assist you. If it's something beyond my scope, I recommend reaching out to our Ad Support team at adsupport@newsbreak.com for further assistance.

I understand you're looking for human assistance. While I can't connect you directly to a live agent, I recommend reaching out to our Ad Support team at adsupport@newsbreak.com. They will be able to provide the help you need.

- Company's full address
